PostureAI: Privacy policy

The app collects, during account creation, the user's name and email address. They are stored on our server and are used to let them log in and to have a personalised user experience. None of this information is shared outside of our company. 

Permissions required by the app:

android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOCATION
android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION 

These permissions are required in order to locate and connect to the PostureSense sensor via bluetooth.